                        <r3d:remarks>FDZ Bildung is a member of the RatSWD research data  infrastructure. FDZ Bildung uses Data Documentation Initiative (DDI) metadata standards.
The Research Data Centre for Education (Forschungsdatenzentrum (FDZ) Bildung) promotes the scientific reusage of research data in educational research. The Database for School Quality (Datenbank zur Qualität von Schule – DaQs) is part of its portfolio.
FDZ Bildung is part of Forschungsdaten Bildung.</r3d:remarks>
